-- Kemper Says Superstorm Sandy Fourth-Quarter Loss Is $45 Million
-- B y   S u s a n n a   P a k
-- 2012-11-20T22:17:14Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-11-20/kemper-says-superstorm-sandy-fourth-quarter-loss-is-45-million.html
Kemper Corp., the Chicago-based
insurer, said pretax catastrophe losses from superstorm Sandy
will be $45 million.  The losses will be included in fourth-quarter earnings,
Kemper said today in a statement distributed by  Business Wire .  To contact the reporter on this story:
